//   * Defensive Postgres date-parsing (Nakama's "no disabled" sentinel
//     is `'1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC'` — we keep the same predicate)
//   * Two-tier fallback: pg_trgm SQL → ILIKE-only SQL → usersGetUsername
